Image Handling
Upload Requirements

Max file size: 2MB per image
Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, WebP
Client-side compression before upload
Auto-generate thumbnails (400px width)
Storage structure: /photos/YYYY/MM/[timestamp]-[filename]

Compression Settings
